To Doc:<br>
     I am not suggesting we deviate from Vietnam at all, I came here to discuss Vietnam only, not Desert Storm or any other issue.  I am not sure how you came to that conclusion, but I am very sorry you did.  I seek answers as well as discussion on Vietnam just as much as you do.  You don't know my interest in the topic and I value the voices of the many vets like yourself, who add to my understanding of the feelings of the time.  My idea is not to change this site from Vietnam to anything, I can read the title and understand its meaning.  <br>
